1
00:00:58,080 --> 00:00:59,200
Hurry up, hurry up

2
00:00:59,680 --> 00:01:00,960
What, did none of you eat?

3
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:02,560
Put some muscle into it

4
00:01:03,160 --> 00:01:05,040
Town Chief, Town Chief, I beg you

5
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:06,800
Please spare my husband

6
00:01:06,800 --> 00:01:08,760
It's not that I won't spare him

7
00:01:09,040 --> 00:01:10,400
Your man has the plague

8
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:11,440
He's already beyond saving

9
00:01:11,440 --> 00:01:12,640
No medicine can cure him now

10
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:14,200
If I don't burn him clean

11
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:16,360
he'll doom everyone in this town

12
00:01:16,360 --> 00:01:17,440
No, no

13
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:19,240
Town Chief, Town Chief, I beg you

14
00:01:19,880 --> 00:01:20,720
I beg you... Are you blind?

15
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:21,960
Get her out of here, Jiang Xianren

16
00:01:22,360 --> 00:01:23,640
I'll pay, I'm begging you

17
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:25,960
Use a Herbal bath to save my husband

18
00:01:25,960 --> 00:01:27,480
No, no

19
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:28,320
Move faster

20
00:01:33,480 --> 00:01:34,600
Hurry up

21
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:36,040
Husband

22
00:01:39,720 --> 00:01:41,720
Master Ai, what brings you here in person?

23
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,400
Merely burning the sick to death

24
00:01:43,600 --> 00:01:45,480
won't completely stop the plague

25
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:47,160
I am a kindhearted man

26
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,440
I cannot bear the world's suffering

27
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:50,280
Allow me to help rid you of this plague

28
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:53,400
Master Ai, you've thought of everything

29
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:55,720
I thank you for the people of Nanwan Town

30
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:57,960
Just thanking me with words?

31
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:58,640
Well...

32
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:02,600
Master Ai

33
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,320
A small token

34
00:02:04,320 --> 00:02:05,280
Just a humble gesture

35
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:11,640
Your husband's life is worth only this

36
00:02:11,640 --> 00:02:12,720
If you keep making a scene

37
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:13,760
you won't even get this

38
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:30,560
A grave on open flatland

39
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:32,160
No water, exposed to wind on all sides

40
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:33,480
This place lacks metal and water

41
00:02:33,480 --> 00:02:35,040
Iron rods must be placed around it

42
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:36,200
Set four bowls of water at the corners

43
00:02:36,880 --> 00:02:38,720
Do as Master Ai says, quick

44
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,160
Prepare to light it

45
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:48,960
Quick

46
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:07,560
Th-This... quick, quick, quick

47
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:10,160
What's going on? Why is the paper figure moving?

48
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:12,400
A ghost! A ghost! Run!

49
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:20,640
Li Zhong, this...

50
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,400
Li Zhong has come to claim lives

51
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:25,600
Jiang Xianren, what do we do?

52
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:27,680
Quick, quick, think of something

53
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,000
This is bad

54
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:31,360
A dire omen

55
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:35,160
It is Li Zhong, burned alive by villagers 12 years ago

56
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:37,360
He has returned through the paper figure

57
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:39,280
What should we do, Immortal?

58
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:49,280
Zheng Yu

59
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,840
Zheng Yu, three, two, one, hit

60
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,760
My butt

61
00:03:58,800 --> 00:03:59,960
My butt

62
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,840
Zheng Yu, you tricked me again

63
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:12,240
Darn it, a paper figure can't have its eyes dotted

64
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,320
Once the eyes are dotted

65
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,720
it will absorb that person's yang energy

66
00:04:14,720 --> 00:04:15,440
and use it to return from the dead

67
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:19,720
Y-You're not scaring me, right?

68
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,640
Y-You'd better burn it now

69
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:23,440
Burn it

70
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:24,400
Burn it up

71
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:28,440
Burn it, burn it

72
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:30,520
It'll come for you at midnight

73
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:34,240
You have to help me, Brother Zheng Yu

74
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,080
Help me break this curse

75
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:37,280
As for me

76
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:40,040
I do have a way to lift the curse for you

77
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:41,600
But I don't have time right now

78
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,680
I need to investigate the Wang family now

79
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,760
We'll talk when I have time

80
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,240
I'll investigate for you

81
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,640
I'll investigate the Wang family for you

82
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,760
Th-This, this, you have to resolve it

83
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:52,080
Deal

84
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,520
Now help me find out quickly

85
00:04:54,520 --> 00:04:55,920
where the Wang family's monster is hiding

86
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:57,560
The monster, right

87
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,840
Didn't that monster already disappear?

88
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:01,320
Why should I keep looking for it?

89
00:05:06,640 --> 00:05:08,120
Until we meet again

90
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:13,200
Until we meet again

91
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:21,000
The Wang family will sacrifice Xunan

92
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:22,360
Take her away

93
00:05:23,080 --> 00:05:24,440
Time is running short

94
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:26,600
We must find the monster's whereabouts fast

95
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:30,800
Whether the curse can be broken depends on you

96
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,000
The Town Chief wants you to gather bones

97
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:36,040
Seems something big happened in town

98
00:05:36,880 --> 00:05:37,560
Something big

99
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,160
The Fifth Concubine does not wish to see you

100
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:45,120
A little maid dares to stop me

101
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:47,120
I am Master Wang's in-law

102
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:48,480
I know who you are

103
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:49,480
The Fifth Concubine said

104
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,480
she does not want to see you

105
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:56,200
Fifth Concubine

106
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:01,000
Zhao Xunan, you heartless thing

107
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:04,240
Your brother is so ill, and you live in comfort

108
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:06,920
I told you long ago

109
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:09,320
Once I married into the Wang family, we were done

110
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,680
Are you still thinking of that filthy bone collector

111
00:06:13,760 --> 00:06:16,640
I had you marry into the Wangs for your own good

112
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:18,280
For my own good

113
00:06:18,840 --> 00:06:21,480
My sister and I were only your tools for profit

114
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,880
When my sister died back then

115
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:26,360
all you knew was to demand compensation from them

116
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:28,480
You did not shed a single tear

117
00:06:29,840 --> 00:06:31,760
The dead cannot come back to life

118
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:34,000
I did it for our family too

119
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,280
You came here today

120
00:06:35,280 --> 00:06:37,520
to squeeze some benefit out of me again, right

121
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:42,320
Your brother gets a herbal bath at Jiang Xianren's daily

122
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,920
That costs quite a lot

123
00:06:44,280 --> 00:06:47,200
I only came to you because I had no other way

124
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:50,960
Enough

125
00:06:52,840 --> 00:06:54,280
I had a master look into it

126
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:56,720
Your father's grave has bad feng shui

127
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:57,880
It brings harm to his children

128
00:06:58,720 --> 00:07:01,960
Otherwise your brother would not stay so sick

129
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:04,280
And your sister too... What are you trying to say

130
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:13,800
Can you ask Zheng Yu to gather your father's bones

131
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:19,640
Do you not find that laughable

132
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:22,480
Back then, you said he was bad luck

133
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:25,720
Now you need him, and call it a feng shui issue

134
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,040
If you want him, invite him yourself

135
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:27,840
I cannot

136
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:34,240
Xunan, it was all my fault back then

137
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:37,760
But your father was never unkind to you

138
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:40,200
Can you really bear

139
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:46,000
to leave him restless in the underworld

140
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:00,920
You should go back first

141
00:08:17,880 --> 00:08:18,920
What brings Master Ai here

142
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:21,560
Of course I came to see you

143
00:08:21,840 --> 00:08:24,560
So many strange and eerie things happened in Nanwan Town

144
00:08:24,640 --> 00:08:26,360
Which of them is more worth seeing than me

145
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:29,280
Did you not say you would teach me bone-gathering

146
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:31,440
Why are you backing out now

147
00:08:32,040 --> 00:08:34,480
When did I ever agree to teach you bone-gathering

148
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:36,120
A young girl like you should not

149
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,160
Did I not tell you that

150
00:08:37,160 --> 00:08:38,360
Being a feng shui master is good enough

151
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:39,400
Do not learn this

152
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:47,560
This is my master's keepsake. Do not touch it

153
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:51,760
So it is a keepsake

154
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:53,560
No wonder it cannot be touched

155
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,800
Brother Zheng Yu

156
00:08:58,920 --> 00:09:00,880
I can be your assistant today

157
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:03,640
I have already chosen the reburial site

158
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:06,080
The Town Chief said there cannot be a single mistake

159
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:07,400
All right, fine

160
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:19,840
The number of bones is off.

161
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:22,360
Didn't the Town Chief say five people?

162
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:23,600
Why are there so many extra?

163
00:09:24,560 --> 00:09:26,960
The dying plague victims from nearby areas

164
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,400
were all sent here to be burned.

165
00:09:28,400 --> 00:09:30,480
So it's normal the remains don't match up.

166
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:33,160
True enough.

167
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:37,480
Brother Zheng Yu

168
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,800
Actually, I rather envy you.

169
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:40,560
You envy me?

170
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:44,520
These days, those burning incense aren't always good.

171
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:46,320
And beggars aren't always poor.

172
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:48,360
Everyone wears a fine skin.

173
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:49,920
But not all have a good heart.

174
00:09:49,920 --> 00:09:50,800
I envy you

175
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,960
because dealing with bones and remains

176
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,880
is far simpler than dealing with the living.

177
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:58,760
Didn't expect Master Ai to sound so mature.

178
00:09:58,760 --> 00:10:00,040
I'm not that young.

179
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:01,320
I'm already 16.

180
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:02,480
If I didn't long for freedom,

181
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:03,800
I'd have been married off long ago.

182
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:06,880
Master Ai, why do you

183
00:10:07,160 --> 00:10:08,960
always like wearing gloves?

184
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,840
It's a rule of our school.

185
00:10:13,040 --> 00:10:15,000
My hands can't be shown to others lightly.

186
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:17,280
Unless it's my future husband.

187
00:10:17,680 --> 00:10:19,680
That's the first I've heard of such a rule.

188
00:10:20,640 --> 00:10:21,600
Brother Zheng Yu

189
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:24,040
If you're that interested in my hands,

190
00:10:24,280 --> 00:10:25,480
why don't I marry you?

191
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:32,160
Master Ai, that's a bit too big a joke.

192
00:10:32,160 --> 00:10:33,480
I'm not joking.

193
00:10:33,680 --> 00:10:35,520
A Bone collector and a feng shui master

194
00:10:35,520 --> 00:10:37,040
the two of us are a perfect match.

195
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:39,080
Brother Zheng Yu

196
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:43,120
If you dare take these gloves off me,

197
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:44,520
then I'll marry you.
